== 事故 ==
2019年10月15日，[[瑞士航空|瑞士航空]]宣布将旗下所有的A220共29架停飞以接受引擎安全检查<ref>{{Cite web|title=Swiss grounds A220 fleet for engine checks|url=https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/business/flight-cancellations_swiss-grounds-a220-fleet-for-engine-checks/45300360|accessdate=2019-10-15|last=swissinfo.ch|first=S. W. I.|work=SWI swissinfo.ch|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200620024459/https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/business/flight-cancellations_swiss-grounds-a220-fleet-for-engine-checks/45300360|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该公司在當年7月25日即发生过一起引擎涡扇碎片脱落、引擎空中停机<ref>{{Cite web|title=Incident: Swiss BCS3 near Paris on Jul 25th 2019, engine shut down in flight|url=https://avherald.com/h?article=4cac778d&opt=0|accessdate=2019-10-16|work=avherald.com|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324015055/http://avherald.com/h?article=4cac778d&opt=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>的事件，当时涉事A220正在执飞日内瓦-伦敦航线，引擎碎片掉落在巴黎上空、飞机备降[[巴黎戴高乐机场|巴黎戴高乐机场]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Bloomberg - Are you a robot?|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=b3f62530-ef61-11e9-8bce-45b93dd315d5&url=L25ld3MvYXJ0aWNsZXMvMjAxOS0xMC0xNC9odW1hbi1ndWluZWEtcGlncy1wcmVwYXJlLWZvci0yMC1ob3VyLW1hcmF0aG9uLWZsaWdodHM=|accessdate=2019-10-15|work=www.bloomberg.com}}</ref>。10月15日当天，有一架航班号LX359、伦敦飞往日内瓦的A220也因为引擎空中停机紧急备降巴黎，[[瑞士航空|瑞士航空]]随即决定立刻停飞旗下A220全系，当时尚有3架正在执飞的航班，分别在完成当次飞行后退出服务<ref>{{Cite web|title=Swiss is grounding its A220 fleet for inspections, saying ‘ongoing technical inspections of several aircraft will restrict our flight operations’. Media reports indicate the grounding is due to another incident — LX359 diverted to Paris earlier today. https://www.flightradar24.com/data/flights/lx359#227ad6ee …pic.twitter.com/aB1TApbwIF|url=https://twitter.com/flightradar24/status/1184118537427791873|accessdate=2019-10-15|date=2019-10-15|last=Flightradar24|work=@flightradar24|language=en|archive-date=2019-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191015162536/https://twitter.com/flightradar24/status/1184118537427791873|dead-url=no}}</ref>。瑞航宣布将全面检查A220系飞机引擎（普惠[[PW1000G|PW1000G]]），部分原定执飞班次可能会被取消。空客表示会全力帮助瑞航减少损失和协助调查<ref>{{Cite news|title=Airline Swiss grounds A220 fleet for engine checks: newspaper|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/us-airbus-swiss-idUKKBN1WU21U|newspaper=Reuters|date=2019-10-15|accessdate=2019-10-15|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917172016/https://uk.reuters.com/article/us-airbus-swiss-idUKKBN1WU21U|dead-url=no}}</ref>。FAA协助了瑞航调查，瑞航宣布在17日开始逐渐恢复A220执飞<ref>{{Cite web|title=Swiss gradually starts returning A220s to flight status|url=https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/swiss-gradually-starts-returning-a220s-to-flight-sta-461509/|accessdate=2019-10-16|date=2019-10-15|last=Kaminski-Morrow|first=David|work=Flightglobal.com|language=en-GB|archive-date=2019-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022100857/https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/swiss-gradually-starts-returning-a220s-to-flight-sta-461509/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。所有的涉事飞机均为A220-300型号。

